  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:12px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:8px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;background:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.02);font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">前两天发完《<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNDQxOTU2MQ==&amp;mid=2247509609&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=8f5767c0209e287d8a15d0c59bc93570&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"邪修版「豆包手机」\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">邪修版「豆包手机」</a>》，反响超预期</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\"></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但很多朋友表示：安装有困难，于是我昨天跑了趟智谱，找到了刘潇</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">刘潇是 AutoGLM 的开发者，本身也是个邪修</span></strong></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&amp;mid=2247492407&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ddf30daa1e30f788e40b9e44449e6bf1&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" imgurl=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2icSMc1VBIYpL8ogbuM1ERXAhanKfuBRQIeeqHOoInxzNvI7ThcA0971CalFzT5GcH7AdPDAOb1nnN8nLDsoOzQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" linktype=\"image\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" target=\"_blank\" data-linktype=\"1\"><span style=\"width:100%;\" class=\"js_jump_icon h5_image_link\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"728\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2icSMc1VBIYpL8ogbuM1ERXAhanKfuBRQIeeqHOoInxzNvI7ThcA0971CalFzT5GcH7AdPDAOb1nnN8nLDsoOzQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100025985\" data-ratio=\"1.33359375\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=eb8f1bf5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F2icSMc1VBIYpL8ogbuM1ERXAhanKfuBRQIeeqHOoInxzNvI7ThcA0971CalFzT5GcH7AdPDAOb1nnN8nLDsoOzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></a>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">刘潇日常懒得打字，桌面上摆了个麦克风，<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyMzI3NzQ0Mg==&amp;mid=2247492407&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ddf30daa1e30f788e40b9e44449e6bf1&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"直接语音输入\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">直接语音输入</a></span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">我俩邪修碰到一起，事情就开始变味了</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“很多人想玩 AutoGLM，但不会装环境”</span></code><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“我们把文档改改，让 AI 能看懂，专门给 Claude Code 读”</span></code><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“搞！”</span></code></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">于是花了一晚上</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">把部署文档重搞了一遍，专门给 AI 看</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\">就放在 README 里，章节名直接叫</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-weight:400;font-size:14.4px;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:4px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;border-style:solid;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:3px 5px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-decoration-style:initial;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;font-feature-settings:normal;opacity:0.9;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">「自动化部署指南（面向 AI）」</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"374\" data-backw=\"546\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYpL8ogbuM1ERXAhanKfuBRQS3DDKJb6qicK9ghGbK39TDwL1EyfMEfJkZvyykiamVBaWdbFovPBkmcQ/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-imgfileid=\"100025974\" data-ratio=\"0.6842961757526445\" data-s=\"300,640\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2458\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95703afe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYpL8ogbuM1ERXAhanKfuBRQS3DDKJb6qicK9ghGbK39TDwL1EyfMEfJkZvyykiamVBaWdbFovPBkmcQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">README 截图：自动化部署指南（面向 AI）</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">里面写清楚了：</span><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么装依赖</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">怎么连手机</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"padding:3px 5px;color:rgb(17, 114, 221);font-size:14.4px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;box-sizing:border-box;font-variation-settings:normal;border-radius:4px;font-feature-settings:normal;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&